info.name: Impulsive Maneuvers
info.oracle_text: Whenever a creature attacks, flip a coin. If you win the flip, the next time that creature would deal combat damage this turn, it deals double that damage instead. If you lose the flip, the next time that creature would deal combat damage this turn, prevent that damage.

info.name: Mogg Assassin
info.oracle_text: {T}: You choose target creature an opponent controls, and that opponent chooses target creature. Flip a coin. If you win the flip, destroy the creature you chose. If you lose the flip, destroy the creature your opponent chose.

info.name: Planar Chaos
info.oracle_text:

name: Heads I Win, Tails You Lose (Secret Lair Commander 2021 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Mirror March
info.oracle_text: Whenever a nontoken creature you control enters, flip a coin until you lose a flip. For each flip you won, create a token that's a copy of that creature. Those tokens gain haste. Exile them at the beginning of the next end step.

name: Heads I Win, Tails You Lose (Secret Lair Commander 2021 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Risky Move
info.oracle_text:
At the beginning of each player's upkeep, that player gains control of Risky Move.
When you gain control of Risky Move from another player, choose a creature you control and an opponent. Flip a coin. If you lose the flip, that opponent gains control of that creature.

info.oracle_text: Choose a number. Flip a coin that many times or until you lose a flip, whichever comes first. If you win all the flips, draw two cards for each flip.
